sequenceDiagram
  participant HTTP as API /rag/ingest
  participant PREP as PreparedAsyncIngestionExecutionService
  participant ENQ as PreparedAsyncIngestionExecutionService.schedule
  participant MQP as Fila pai Dramatiq
  participant WP as Worker pai
  participant FAN as DocumentFanoutCoordinator
  participant MQC as Fila filha Dramatiq
  participant WC as Worker filho
  participant PDF as Pipeline PDF
  participant IDX as Indexacao final

  HTTP->>PREP: valida request e compoe YAML
  PREP->>ENQ: schedule_prepared_ingestion_worker_job()
  ENQ->>MQP: publica envelope prepared_yaml
  MQP->>WP: entrega job pai
  WP->>FAN: build_plan() quando fan-out e elegivel
  FAN->>MQC: publica envelopes document_fanout_child
  MQC->>WC: entrega documento filho
  WC->>PDF: executa slice PDF do documento
  PDF->>IDX: devolve chunks para indexacao
  IDX-->>WC: persistencia e telemetria terminal
